Kind Regards,
Isha

Hi, 

I have raised a complaint regarding the blood samples collected today by your technician R.K.Jaiswal.

The reports generated on your pharmeasy app shows wrong tests displayed in my and my husband's report.

Please correct our reports as per below names and tests as booked in the app on 4th Dec,

Ashish Tyagi - Men's Wellness Health Package, Lipase test, Amylase test

Isha Monish - Women's Master Checkup with Cancer & Arthritis, Fasting Blood Sugar, Urine Routine test


Please correct the reports and name in the reports on urgent basis as above information.

Also, I would like to formally escalate this issue in tests and names has been done by your technician R.K. Jaiswal.
He took extra money in the name of including fasting blood sugar and urine routine tests for me as he said that these two tests are not included in the Women's Master checkup though these tests were already there.

For my husband, I have paid 2267 instead of 1599 as the technician told me to include Lipase and Amylase test.

Attaching payment screenshot done on the technician's personal no.

Please do help urgently on the same.


Kind Regards,
Isha
